{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"238cee9d6e5d3351d1562b","title":"按键发声蜂鸣与等待旋律开发记录","desc":"","updated":1780371367059,"created":1780371330025,"custom":{},"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.2026-05-18_按键发声蜂鸣与等待旋律开发记录","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"0faeb5e2eb464db690255a82c63340b6","links":[{"from":{"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机","id":"bk7252n-ai-printer","vaultName":"Dendron"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":3,"offset":1127},"end":{"line":32,"column":55,"offset":1179},"indent":[]},"value":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.2026-05-18_按键发声蜂鸣与等待旋律开发记录"},{"from":{"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.2026-05-27_蜂鸣旋律MQTT协同与TCM内存优化开发记录","id":"8e26e8749bccd9d3739356","vaultName":"Dendron"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":10,"offset":149},"end":{"line":7,"column":62,"offset":201},"indent":[]},"value":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.2026-05-18_按键发声蜂鸣与等待旋律开发记录"}],"anchors":{"按键发声蜂鸣与等待旋律开发记录":{"type":"header","text":"按键发声蜂鸣与等待旋律开发记录","value":"按键发声蜂鸣与等待旋律开发记录","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"1-背景":{"type":"header","text":"1. 背景","value":"1-背景","line":16,"column":0,"depth":2},"2-改动文件清单":{"type":"header","text":"2. 改动文件清单","value":"2-改动文件清单","line":28,"column":0,"depth":2},"3-技术方案":{"type":"header","text":"3. 技术方案","value":"3-技术方案","line":41,"column":0,"depth":2},"31-统一常驻音频线程架构":{"type":"header","text":"3.1 统一常驻音频线程架构","value":"31-统一常驻音频线程架构","line":43,"column":0,"depth":3},"32-叮咚双音蜂鸣":{"type":"header","text":"3.2 \"叮咚\"双音蜂鸣","value":"32-叮咚双音蜂鸣","line":57,"column":0,"depth":3},"33-等待旋律c大调琶音":{"type":"header","text":"3.3 等待旋律（C大调琶音）","value":"33-等待旋律c大调琶音","line":95,"column":0,"depth":3},"34-静音控制":{"type":"header","text":"3.4 静音控制","value":"34-静音控制","line":118,"column":0,"depth":3},"35-音量控制":{"type":"header","text":"3.5 音量控制","value":"35-音量控制","line":131,"column":0,"depth":3},"4-与按键模块的集成":{"type":"header","text":"4. 与按键模块的集成","value":"4-与按键模块的集成","line":142,"column":0,"depth":2},"41-按键发声":{"type":"header","text":"4.1 按键发声","value":"41-按键发声","line":144,"column":0,"depth":3},"42-静音与录音联动":{"type":"header","text":"4.2 静音与录音联动","value":"42-静音与录音联动","line":165,"column":0,"depth":3},"43-系统初始化":{"type":"header","text":"4.3 系统初始化","value":"43-系统初始化","line":177,"column":0,"depth":3},"5-编译期开关":{"type":"header","text":"5. 编译期开关","value":"5-编译期开关","line":190,"column":0,"depth":2},"6-注意事项与已知约束":{"type":"header","text":"6. 注意事项与已知约束","value":"6-注意事项与已知约束","line":198,"column":0,"depth":2},"7-相关源码路径":{"type":"header","text":"7. 相关源码路径","value":"7-相关源码路径","line":212,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"xsq1mkrqaj59l9qxnxi8lpj","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"按键发声蜂鸣与等待旋律开发记录\">按键发声蜂鸣与等待旋律开发记录<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#按键发声蜂鸣与等待旋律开发记录\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"按键发声蜂鸣与等待旋律开发记录-1\">按键发声蜂鸣与等待旋律开发记录<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#按键发声蜂鸣与等待旋律开发记录-1\"></a></h1>\n<p><strong>日期</strong>：2026-05-18<br>\n<strong>工程</strong>：<code>bk7252n_sdk-SDK_3.0.76.1_witch_lcd</code><br>\n<strong>编译命令</strong>：<code>scons --beken=bk7252n -j4</code></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"1-背景\">1. 背景<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#1-背景\"></a></h2>\n<p>此前按键操作（单击/长按/松开）无任何声音反馈，用户体验生硬。为提升产品交互质感，需要：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>按键按下时发出短促提示音</strong>，让用户明确感知按键已被触发；</li>\n<li><strong>语音录音期间自动静音按键提示音</strong>，避免\"滴滴\"声混入语音上传数据；</li>\n<li><strong>云端生图等待期间播放循环旋律</strong>，替代死板的静默等待，增强陪伴感。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>目标用户为 <strong>6-10 岁儿童</strong>，提示音需有\"玩具感\"而非生硬的电子蜂鸣。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"2-改动文件清单\">2. 改动文件清单<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2-改动文件清单\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>文件</th><th>改动类型</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>applications/button_control/beep.h</code></td><td><strong>新增</strong></td><td>蜂鸣与旋律模块头文件，暴露 <code>beep_init()</code> / <code>beep_play()</code> / <code>beep_set_muted()</code> / <code>beep_melody_start()</code> / <code>beep_melody_stop()</code> / <code>beep_set_volume()</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/button_control/beep.c</code></td><td><strong>新增</strong></td><td>统一常驻音频线程实现：DAC 驱动、命令+信号量调度、\"叮咚\"双音合成、循环旋律播放、静音/音量控制</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/button_control/melody_pcm_data.h</code></td><td><strong>新增</strong></td><td>预生成的等待旋律 PCM 数据（C大调琶音，8000Hz int16_t，34400 采样 ≈ 4.3s），Flash 常量零 RAM 开销</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/button_control/button_control.c</code></td><td>修改</td><td><code>button_press_down()</code> 中调用 <code>beep_play()</code>；P37 录音启动/结束时调用 <code>beep_set_muted()</code> 控制静音</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/button_control/SConscript</code></td><td>修改</td><td>新增 <code>drivers/audio</code>、<code>func/vad</code> 等头文件路径依赖</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/main.c</code></td><td>修改</td><td>系统初始化阶段调用 <code>beep_init()</code> 创建常驻音频线程</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"3-技术方案\">3. 技术方案<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#3-技术方案\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"31-统一常驻音频线程架构\">3.1 统一常驻音频线程架构<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#31-统一常驻音频线程架构\"></a></h3>\n<p>采用 <strong>单一常驻线程 + 命令/信号量</strong> 模式，替代早期双线程方案：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>线程名</strong>：<code>\"audio_th\"</code>，栈 4096B，优先级 27</li>\n<li><strong>命令枚举</strong>：<code>BEEP_CMD_NONE</code> / <code>BEEP_CMD_PLAY</code> / <code>BEEP_CMD_MELODY_START</code> / <code>BEEP_CMD_MELODY_STOP</code></li>\n<li><strong>调度方式</strong>：各 API 写入 <code>s_cmd</code> 后 <code>rt_sem_release</code> 唤醒线程；线程处理完后将 <code>s_cmd</code> 复位为 <code>BEEP_CMD_NONE</code></li>\n<li><strong>初始化</strong>：<code>beep_init()</code> 由 <code>main.c</code> 在系统启动阶段调用，创建信号量和线程，并预分配蜂鸣 PCM 缓冲区</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>优势</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>消除双线程的栈开销（原 2×2048 = 4096B → 现单线程 4096B，实际节省了线程控制块等元数据）</li>\n<li>命令互斥天然保证 DAC 不并发争抢</li>\n<li>旋律停止时通过 <code>rt_sem_release</code> 立即唤醒（不再依赖轮询标志位延时）</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"32-叮咚双音蜂鸣\">3.2 \"叮咚\"双音蜂鸣<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#32-叮咚双音蜂鸣\"></a></h3>\n<p>采用 <strong>PCM 直灌 DAC</strong> 方案，绕过 MP3 解码器，彻底规避栈溢出风险（此前 MP3 提示音曾因 <code>minimp3</code> 栈上大结构体导致 <code>auprompt</code> 线程栈溢出死机）。</p>\n<p><strong>音色设计</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>高音段（\"叮\"）</strong>：667Hz 正弦波 @ 8000Hz 采样率，12 采样点/周期，循环 55 周期 ≈ 83ms</li>\n<li><strong>低音段（\"咚\"）</strong>：500Hz 正弦波 @ 8000Hz 采样率，16 采样点/周期，循环 45 周期 ≈ 90ms</li>\n<li><strong>总时长</strong> ≈ 173ms，类似玩具门铃的\"叮咚\"效果，适合儿童产品</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>PCM 数据</strong>（编译期常量，存 Flash）：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* 667Hz 正弦波，12 采样点/周期 */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">int16_t</span> BEEP_PCM_HIGH<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token number\">0x0000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x4000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x6EDA</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x7FFF</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token number\">0x6EDA</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x4000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x0000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xC000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token number\">0x9126</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x8001</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x9126</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xC000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* 500Hz 正弦波，16 采样点/周期 */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">int16_t</span> BEEP_PCM_LOW<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token number\">0x0000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x30FB</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x5A82</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x7641</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token number\">0x7FFF</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x7641</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x5A82</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x30FB</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token number\">0x0000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xCF05</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xA57E</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x89BF</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token number\">0x8001</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x89BF</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xA57E</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xCF05</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>播放流程</strong>（在 <code>audio_th</code> 线程中执行）：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>收到 <code>BEEP_CMD_PLAY</code> 命令后，打开 <code>\"sound\"</code> DAC 设备，设置 8000Hz 采样率</li>\n<li>使用线程启动时预分配的 <code>beep_buf</code>（已填充高音段+低音段 PCM）</li>\n<li>保存并清除 <code>tx_complete</code> 回调，<code>rt_device_write</code> 一次性写入全部 PCM 数据</li>\n<li>延时 200ms 等待 DAC FIFO 排空</li>\n<li>恢复 <code>tx_complete</code> 回调，关闭 DAC</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>资源占用</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Flash：约 56B（两段正弦波常量）</li>\n<li>RAM：<code>beep_buf</code> 约 2.4KB（线程生命周期内常驻），线程栈 4KB（与旋律共用）</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"33-等待旋律c大调琶音\">3.3 等待旋律（C大调琶音）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#33-等待旋律c大调琶音\"></a></h3>\n<p><strong>用途</strong>：云端 AI 生图期间替代静默等待，循环播放至生图完成。</p>\n<p><strong>旋律数据</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>预生成 C大调琶音 PCM，8000Hz mono int16_t</li>\n<li>34400 采样 ≈ 4.3 秒/循环</li>\n<li>存为 Flash 常量 <code>MELODY_PCM[]</code>（<code>melody_pcm_data.h</code>），零 RAM 占用</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>播放流程</strong>（在 <code>audio_th</code> 线程中执行）：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>收到 <code>BEEP_CMD_MELODY_START</code> 命令后，设置 <code>s_melody_running = RT_TRUE</code></li>\n<li>打开 DAC，设置 8000Hz，音量取全局音量的 70%（更柔和）</li>\n<li>预填 2 份 PCM 数据到 DAC FIFO（消除段间间隙）</li>\n<li>循环：通过 <code>rt_sem_take(&#x26;s_audio_sem, timeout)</code> 以 200ms 为粒度等待约 4.1s，超时后补写 1 份 PCM</li>\n<li>收到 <code>BEEP_CMD_MELODY_STOP</code> 时，<code>s_melody_running</code> 置为 <code>RT_FALSE</code>，同时 <code>rt_sem_release</code> 立即唤醒线程中的超时等待</li>\n<li>关闭 DAC，线程回到等待命令状态</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>关键设计</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>s_melody_running</code> 用 <code>volatile rt_bool_t</code> 保证跨线程可见</li>\n<li>预填 2 份消除循环段间的静音间隙</li>\n<li>停止时通过信号量立即唤醒（不再仅依赖轮询标志位延时），响应更快</li>\n<li>音量取全局 70%，避免旋律盖过其它提示音</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"34-静音控制\">3.4 静音控制<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#34-静音控制\"></a></h3>\n<p>语音交互期间（P37 长按录音→上传→等待识别结果），按键\"滴滴\"声会混入录音数据，干扰 ASR 识别。</p>\n<p><strong>方案</strong>：全局静音标志 <code>s_beep_muted</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>时机</th><th>操作</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>P37 长按、录音启动成功后</td><td><code>beep_set_muted(RT_TRUE)</code> — 抑制后续按键发声</td></tr><tr><td>P37 松开、录音停止后</td><td><code>beep_set_muted(RT_FALSE)</code> — 恢复按键发声</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p><code>beep_play()</code> 和 <code>beep_melody_start()</code> 均在入口处检查静音标志，若静音则直接返回不发声。</p>\n<h3 id=\"35-音量控制\">3.5 音量控制<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#35-音量控制\"></a></h3>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">beep_set_volume</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> volume<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// 范围 0~100，默认 65</span>\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>当前实现为占位函数（仅钳位参数范围），后续可接入 <code>CODEC_CMD_SET_VOLUME</code> 设置 DAC 硬件音量</li>\n<li>旋律音量自动取全局音量的 70%（在调用 DAC 写入前逻辑控制）</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"4-与按键模块的集成\">4. 与按键模块的集成<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#4-与按键模块的集成\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"41-按键发声\">4.1 按键发声<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#41-按键发声\"></a></h3>\n<p>在 <code>button_control.c</code> 的 <code>button_press_down()</code> 回调中：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">button_press_down</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>param<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token class-name\">uint8_t</span> gpio <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">button_get_trigger_gpio</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>param<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// P13（休眠键）不发声</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>gpio <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> BUTTON_GPIO_P13<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// 等待识别结果或打印中不发声</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token function\">audio_result_wait_is_locked</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;&#x26;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token function\">thermal_printer_is_printing</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">beep_play</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>锁判断逻辑</strong>：与单击/长按回调保持一致——<code>audio_result_wait_is_locked()</code> 或 <code>thermal_printer_is_printing()</code> 任一为真时，不发声也不执行业务逻辑，避免打断关键流程。</p>\n<h3 id=\"42-静音与录音联动\">4.2 静音与录音联动<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#42-静音与录音联动\"></a></h3>\n<p>在 <code>button_long_press_start()</code>（P37 长按）和 <code>button_press_up()</code>（P37 松开）中：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token comment\">// P37 长按 → 录音启动成功后</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">beep_set_muted</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>RT_TRUE<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// P37 松开 → 录音停止后</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">beep_set_muted</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>RT_FALSE<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"43-系统初始化\">4.3 系统初始化<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#43-系统初始化\"></a></h3>\n<p><code>main.c</code> 在系统启动阶段调用：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">beep_init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">rt_kprintf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"beep_init failed\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p><code>beep_init()</code> 创建信号量 <code>\"beep_sem\"</code> 并启动常驻 <code>\"audio_th\"</code> 线程，预分配蜂鸣 PCM 缓冲区。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"5-编译期开关\">5. 编译期开关<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#5-编译期开关\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>宏</th><th>默认值</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>CFG_BEEP_MELODY_ENABLE</code></td><td>1</td><td>旋律功能总开关，定义于 <code>beep.c</code>，设为 0 可编译期裁剪旋律数据和代码</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"6-注意事项与已知约束\">6. 注意事项与已知约束<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#6-注意事项与已知约束\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>DAC 独占</strong>：蜂鸣和旋律共用同一个 <code>\"sound\"</code> DAC 设备，由统一音频线程的命令互斥机制保证同一时刻只有一个在播放。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>无 MP3 依赖</strong>：本方案完全基于 PCM 直灌，不依赖 <code>minimp3</code> 或任何 MP3 解码器，<strong>没有栈溢出风险</strong>。此前 MP3 提示音方案已因 <code>minimp3</code> 栈上数十 KB 的 <code>mp3dec_scratch_t</code> 导致 <code>auprompt</code> 线程栈溢出死机而被移除。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>线程模型</strong>：单一常驻 <code>\"audio_th\"</code> 线程（栈 4096B，优先级 27），低于音频上传等关键业务线程，不会抢占关键资源。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Flash 占用</strong>：旋律 PCM 数据 68.8KB（34400×2），若需裁剪可设置 <code>CFG_BEEP_MELODY_ENABLE=0</code>，或替换为更短的旋律。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>音量控制</strong>：<code>beep_set_volume()</code> 当前为占位实现，未实际控制 DAC 硬件音量。后续可接入 <code>CODEC_CMD_SET_VOLUME</code> 生效。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"7-相关源码路径\">7. 相关源码路径<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#7-相关源码路径\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>用途</th><th>路径</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>蜂鸣/旋律模块</td><td><code>applications/button_control/beep.c</code></td></tr><tr><td>蜂鸣/旋律头文件</td><td><code>applications/button_control/beep.h</code></td></tr><tr><td>旋律 PCM 数据</td><td><code>applications/button_control/melody_pcm_data.h</code></td></tr><tr><td>按键集成（发声/静音调用）</td><td><code>applications/button_control/button_control.c</code></td></tr><tr><td>构建配置</td><td><code>applications/button_control/SConscript</code></td></tr><tr><td>系统初始化调用</td><td><code>applications/main.c</code>（<code>beep_init()</code>）</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<hr>\n<p><em>文档整理日期：2026-05-18；对应工程：<code>bk7252n_sdk-SDK_3.0.76.1_witch_lcd</code>。</em></p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/Dendron/notes/bk7252n-ai-printer\">BK7252N AI 打印机</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Dendron/notes/8e26e8749bccd9d3739356\">蜂鸣/旋律 MQTT 协同与 TCM 内存优化开发记录</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"个人开发笔记","desc":"个人开发笔记（Dendron 多项目知识库）","updated":1780371367067,"created":1595961348801,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"e7a2abab31fd5da92a5ad2e013605349","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"项目","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":3,"offset":41},"end":{"line":6,"column":9,"offset":47},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"项目"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":3,"offset":59},"end":{"line":7,"column":23,"offset":79},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"tutorial","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":3,"offset":128},"end":{"line":11,"column":15,"offset":140},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"tutorial"}}],"anchors":{"项目":{"type":"header","text":"项目","value":"项目","line":10,"column":0,"depth":2},"工作区":{"type":"header","text":"工作区","value":"工作区","line":15,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["c1bs7wsjfbhb0zipaywqv1","projects"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\n按**项目**组织的固件与软件开发文档（Dendron）。\n\n## 项目\n\n- [[项目]] — 全部项目索引\n- [[项目.BK7252N-AI打印机]] — BK7252N AI 打印机固件（RT-Thread + LVGL）\n\n## 工作区\n\n- [[tutorial]] — Dendron 使用教程\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true,"enableSelfContainedVaults":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"vaults":[{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"}],"enableXVaultWikiLink":true,"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"task","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x","assigned":"a","moved":"m","blocked":"b","delegated":"l","dropped":"d","pending":"y"},"taskCompleteStatus":["done","x"],"prioritySymbols":{"H":"high","M":"medium","L":"low"},"todoIntegration":false,"createTaskSelectionType":"selection2link"},"graph":{"zoomSpeed":1,"createStub":false},"enableAutoCreateOnDefinition":false,"enableRemoteVaultInit":true,"enableUserTags":true,"enableHashTags":true,"workspaceVaultSyncMode":"noCommit","enableAutoFoldFrontmatter":false,"enableEditorDecorations":true,"maxPreviewsCached":10,"maxNoteLength":204800,"enableFullHierarchyNoteTitle":false,"enablePersistentHistory":false},"preview":{"enableFMTitle":true,"enableNoteTitleForLink":true,"enableFrontmatterTags":true,"enableHashesForFMTags":false,"enablePrettyRefs":true,"enableKatex":true,"automaticallyShowPreview":false},"publishing":{"enableFMTitle":true,"enableNoteTitleForLink":true,"enablePrettyRefs":true,"enableKatex":true,"copyAssets":true,"siteHierarchies":["root"],"writeStubs":false,"siteRootDir":"docs","seo":{"title":"个人开发笔记","description":"按项目组织的固件与软件开发文档（Dendron）"},"github":{"enableEditLink":true,"editLinkText":"Edit this page on GitHub","editBranch":"main","editViewMode":"tree"},"enableSiteLastModified":true,"enableFrontmatterTags":true,"enableHashesForFMTags":false,"enableRandomlyColoredTags":true,"enableTaskNotes":true,"enablePrettyLinks":true,"searchMode":"search","siteUrl":"https://xiayu12345.github.io","assetsPrefix":"/Dendron","theme":"custom","siteFaviconPath":"favicon.ico","siteIndex":"root"}}},"__N_SSG":true}